adept.kbapi

Class KBOpenIERelation

  • java.lang.Object
    • adept.kbapi.KBPredicateArgument
      • adept.kbapi.KBOpenIERelation

  • public class KBOpenIERelation
extends KBPredicateArgument
    The Class KBOpenIERelation represents a fully loaded, immutable OpenIE relation. The KBID corresponds to the openIERelationID in the OpenIDRelations Postgres table.
    Author:
    dakodes, msrivast
